@piquark6046 Could you please exclude the `investing.com` (I mean add `domain=~investing.com`) from this rule - `||securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/tag/js/gpt.js$script,redirect=googletagservices-gpt` from `List-KR`?
At least until scriptlets library will be updated in apps and extensions to version 1.8.

And maybe also other domains like here - https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/commit/5e77f19d2b0ccd7dbcdc9a58639b696671bc33a6

